<h2>You now have access to a Piessang seller dashboard</h2>

<p>Hi <%= typeof name !== "undefined" && name ? name : (typeof customerName !== "undefined" && customerName ? customerName : "there") %>,</p>

<p>
You have been granted access to the <strong><%= vendorName %></strong> seller account on Piessang.
</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Vendor:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <li><strong>Role:</strong> <%= role %></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
  <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:8px;background:#202020;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;">
    Open seller dashboard
  </a>
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
If the button does not work, copy this link into your browser:<br/>
<%= dashboardUrl %>
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">
Cheers,<br/>
The Piessang Team
</p>
